(12, 1, '2018-09-30 16:19:05', '2018-09-30 16:19:05', '<h3>Die with memories , not dreams.</h3>		\n			<h3>sajek valley</h3>		\n		<p>Sajek Valley is an emerging tourist spot in Bangladesh situated among the hills of Kasalong range of mountains in Sajek union, Baghaichhari Upazila in Rangamati District. The valley is 1,800 feet above sea level. Sajek valley is known as the Queen of Hills &amp; Roof of Rangamati.</p>		\n										<img width=\"2048\" height=\"1166\" src=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/34453821_1092361487577689_1022940151958994944_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/34453821_1092361487577689_1022940151958994944_o.jpg 2048w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/34453821_1092361487577689_1022940151958994944_o-300x171.jpg 300w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/34453821_1092361487577689_1022940151958994944_o-768x437.jpg 768w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/34453821_1092361487577689_1022940151958994944_o-1024x583.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />											\n										<img width=\"2672\" height=\"1504\" src=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMAG4774.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMAG4774.jpg 2672w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMAG4774-300x169.jpg 300w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMAG4774-768x432.jpg 768w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMAG4774-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2672px) 100vw, 2672px\" />											\n			<h3>kaptai lake kayaking</h3>		\n		<p>Kaptai Lake is the largest man made lake in Bangladesh. It is located in the Kaptai Upazila under Rangamati District of Chittagong Division</p>		\n			<h3>coxs bazar sea beach</h3>		\n		<p>Cox\'s Bazar Beach, located at Cox\'s Bazar, Bangladesh, is the longest unbroken sea beach in the world, running 120 kilometres. It is the top tourist destination of Bangladesh.</p>		\n										<img width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2-200x300.jpg 200w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2-768x1152.jpg 768w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/2-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" />											\n			<h3>St. Martin\'s Island</h3>		\n		<p>St. Martin\'s Island is a small island in the northeastern part of the Bay of Bengal, about 9 km south of the tip of the Cox\'s Bazar-Teknaf peninsula, and forming the southernmost part of Bangladesh. There is a small adjoining island that is separated at high tide, called Chera Dwip.</p>		\n										<img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/29749689_1057147281099110_3058812811728504976_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/29749689_1057147281099110_3058812811728504976_o.jpg 2048w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/29749689_1057147281099110_3058812811728504976_o-300x200.jpg 300w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/29749689_1057147281099110_3058812811728504976_o-768x512.jpg 768w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/29749689_1057147281099110_3058812811728504976_o-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" />											\n			<h3>The Best Experiences Ever</h3>		\n		https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yl9nvc6j-9k&#038;feature=youtu.behttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bKwjHGCmriI&#038;t=2shttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T7bSUmGhoVQ&#038;feature=youtu.be		\n							living the dream\n							<img width=\"1365\" height=\"1365\" src=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o.jpg 1365w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o-150x150.jpg 150w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o-300x300.jpg 300w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o-768x768.jpg 768w, http://vamp.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42204400_1205404062940097_5778298581693759488_o-1024x1024.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\" />						\n													Saikat cullen\n																			my life , my rules', 'My memories', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-memories', '', '', '2018-10-01 16:41:00', '2018-10-01 16:41:00', '', 0, 'http://vamp.github.io/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
